query:
INSERT INTO topups (
                card_number,
                topup_amount,
                topup_method,
                topup_time,
                status,
                created_at,
                updated_at
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, 'pending',CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP)
            RETURNING
                topup_id,
                card_number,
                topup_no,
                topup_amount as "topup_amount!",
                topup_method,
                topup_time,
                status,
                created_at,
                updated_at,
                deleted_at
